{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845808960,"sessionID":"ses_2875a3ff6ffeJ8vkKZNGsaUIs0","part":{"id":"prt_d78a89729001vdORQukNOctR0K","messageID":"msg_d78a8900d0013hmLJO0ZafNZoQ","sessionID":"ses_2875a3ff6ffeJ8vkKZNGsaUIs0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_50f2b216ce96453db51b10b2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Idle Cleanup — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module\n4: \n5: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n6: \n7: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n8: \n9: ### Time threshold\n10: \n11: ```go\n12: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n13: ```\n14: \n15: Idle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n16: \n17: ### Annotation key\n18: \n19: The reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n20: \n21: - Import: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n22: - Key: `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` = **`\"last-activity-time\"`**\n23: \n24: (Workload manager also sets `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` on Sandbox metadata for template-driven idle configuration; **agentd** only reads `last-activity-time`.)\n25: \n26: ### Reconciler\n27: \n28: ```go\n29: package agentd\n30: \n31: type Reconciler struct {\n32:     client.Client\n33:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n34: }\n35: \n36: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)\n37: ```\n38: \n39: **Algorithm (exact behavior):**\n40: \n41: 1. `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`; `Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`.\n42: 2. If `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`.\n43: 3. If other get error → return `ctrl.Result{}, err`.\n44: 4. `lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]`.\n45: 5. If `exists && lastActivityStr != \"\"`:\n46:    - `lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)`\n47:    - If parse err → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err`\n48:    - `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`\n49:    - If `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`:\n50:      - `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)`; if err and not `IsNotFound` → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n51:    - Else:\n52:      - `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil`\n53: 6. `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n54: \n55: ### SetupWithManager\n56: \n57: ```go\n58: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n59:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n60:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n61:         Complete(r)\n62: }\n63: ```\n64: \n65: ## Binary `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n66: \n67: ### Scheme registration\n68: \n69: ```go\n70: var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n71: \n72: func init() {\n73:     utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n74:     utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n75: }\n76: ```\n77: \n78: ### Controller-runtime manager\n79: \n80: ```go\n81: mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n82:     Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n83:     Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n84:     HealthProbeBindAddress:   \"0\",\n85: })\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ### Controller registration (duplicate of SetupWithManager pattern)\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: err = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n92:     For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n93:     Complete(&agentd.Reconciler{\n94:         Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n95:         Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n96:     })\n97: ```\n98: \n99: ### Run\n100: \n101: ```go\n102: mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())\n103: ```\n104: \n105: ## Watched resources\n106: \n107: | API group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n108: |-----------|---------|------|---------|\n109: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` | Default `For()` watch — creates, updates, deletes (per controller-runtime) |\n110: \n111: No explicit `Owns` or `Watches` — single primary resource `Sandbox`.\n112: \n113: ## Related workload-manager constants (context)\n114: \n115: From `pkg/workloadmanager` (not used by agentd reconcile logic but set when sandboxes are created):\n116: \n117: - `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"` — duration string on Sandbox CR.\n118: - `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"` — **read by agentd** for idle cleanup.\n119: \n120: ## Dependencies\n121: \n122: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n123: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n124: - `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`\n125: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`\n126: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` (annotation key only)\n\n(End of file - total 126 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Idle Cleanup — Design\n\n## Module\n\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n\n### Time threshold\n\n```go\nvar SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n```\n\nIdle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n\n### Annotation key\n\nThe reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md","time":{"start":1775845808951,"end":1775845808959}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845810254,"sessionID":"ses_2875a3ff6ffeJ8vkKZNGsaUIs0","part":{"id":"prt_d78a89c0b001W4BtXDsI9hvB7Q","messageID":"msg_d78a8900d0013hmLJO0ZafNZoQ","sessionID":"ses_2875a3ff6ffeJ8vkKZNGsaUIs0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_a5c2307201c346c98f4ca8c6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Idle Cleanup Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: Run a controller that deletes `Sandbox` custom resources when an idle-timeout annotation indicates the sandbox has been inactive beyond a fixed grace period.\n5: \n6: ## Requirements\n7: \n8: ### Requirement: Reconciliation trigger\n9: The system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API version `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, using the manager’s API reader/writer client for get/delete operations.\n10: \n11: #### Scenario: Sandbox watch drives reconcile\n12: - **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` object is created or updated in the cluster\n13: - **WHEN** the manager is running\n14: - **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object’s namespace and name\n15: \n16: ### Requirement: Idle detection input\n17: The system SHALL read annotation key `last-activity-time` (constant `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`) from the `Sandbox` metadata. When the annotation is missing or empty, the system SHALL take no delete action and SHALL return without requeue (unless other logic applies—none in this controller).\n18: \n19: #### Scenario: No annotation means no deletion\n20: - **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` without `last-activity-time`\n21: - **WHEN** reconciliation completes\n22: - **THEN** the sandbox is not deleted and result has zero `RequeueAfter`\n23: \n24: ### Requirement: Idle detection parsing\n25: When the annotation is non-empty, the system SHALL parse it with `time.RFC3339`. On parse error, the system SHALL return `RequeueAfter: 30 seconds` and the parse error.\n26: \n27: #### Scenario: Invalid timestamp requeues\n28: - **GIVEN** annotation value is not RFC3339\n29: - **WHEN** `time.Parse` fails\n30: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)`\n31: \n32: ### Requirement: Expiration threshold\n33: The system SHALL define `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`. The system SHALL compute `expirationTime = lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`. When `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`, the system SHALL delete the `Sandbox` resource.\n34: \n35: #### Scenario: Idle beyond 15 minutes triggers delete\n36: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` parses to a time more than 15 minutes in the past\n37: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n38: - **THEN** the controller calls delete on the `Sandbox` client object\n39: \n40: #### Scenario: Not yet expired requeues until expiration\n41: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` is recent enough that expiration is in the future\n42: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n43: - **THEN** the result is `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)` and no delete occurs\n44: \n45: ### Requirement: Delete idempotency\n46: When delete returns `NotFound`, the system SHALL treat it as success and SHALL return empty result with nil error. Other delete errors SHALL be returned to trigger retry.\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: Already deleted sandbox\n49: - **GIVEN** the API server returns not found on delete\n50: - **WHEN** the reconciler handles the error\n51: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n52: \n53: ### Requirement: Get not found\n54: When get returns `NotFound`, the system SHALL return empty result and nil error.\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: Sandbox removed before reconcile\n57: - **GIVEN** the sandbox no longer exists\n58: - **WHEN** `Get` fails with not found\n59: - **THEN** reconcile returns without error\n60: \n61: ## Requirements (binary / operator)\n62: \n63: ### Requirement: Manager options\n64: The `agentd` binary SHALL construct controller-runtime `Manager` with scheme containing core Kubernetes types and `sandboxv1alpha1` from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`, SHALL disable metrics server (`BindAddress: \"0\"`), and SHALL disable health probe server (`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`).\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: Signal-driven shutdown\n67: - **GIVEN** the process runs `mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())`\n68: - **WHEN** SIGTERM/SIGINT is received\n69: - **THEN** the manager stops gracefully per controller-runtime defaults\n\n(End of file - total 69 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Idle Cleanup Specification\n\n## Purpose\nRun a controller that deletes `Sandbox` custom resources when an idle-timeout annotation indicates the sandbox has been inactive beyond a fixed grace period.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Reconciliation trigger\nThe system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API version `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, using the manager’s API reader/writer client for get/delete operations.\n\n#### Scenario: Sandbox watch drives reconcile\n- **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` object is created or updated in the cluster\n- **WHEN** the manager is running\n- **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object’s namespace and name\n\n### Requirement: Idle detection input\nThe system SHALL read annotation key `last-activity-time` (constant `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`) from the `Sandbox` metadata. When the annotation is missing or empty, the system SHALL take no delete action and SHALL return without requeue (unless other logic applies—none in this controller).\n\n#### Scenario: No annotation means no deletion\n- **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` without `last-activity-time`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md","time":{"start":1775845810245,"end":1775845810252}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845811584,"sessionID":"ses_2875a3ff6ffeJ8vkKZNGsaUIs0","part":{"id":"prt_d78a8a0d400171OHXKSGqrSOi1","messageID":"msg_d78a8900d0013hmLJO0ZafNZoQ","sessionID":"ses_2875a3ff6ffeJ8vkKZNGsaUIs0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_af65464f02c345e68c5abb11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/picod\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ## 目的\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube PicoD 沙箱守护进程添加 JWT 认证中间件，确保只有经过 Router 签发的合法请求才能执行命令和访问文件。当前 PicoD 的所有 `/api` 端点缺乏认证保护，任何网络可达的客户端均可直接调用沙箱资源，存在严重的安全风险。\n10: \n11: PicoD 运行在每个沙箱 Pod 内部，负责命令执行和文件管理。由于沙箱网络可能被同一 Namespace 内的其他 Pod 访问，必须通过 JWT 验证请求来源为合法的 Router 实例，防止未授权的沙箱资源滥用。\n12: \n13: ## 范围\n14: \n15: ### 包含\n16: \n17: 1. **AuthManager 实现**\n18:    - `AuthManager` 结构体：持有 RSA 公钥和读写锁，支持线程安全的密钥访问\n19:    - `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()`：从 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量加载 PEM 格式的 RSA 公钥\n20:    - 启动时强制加载公钥，失败则 Fatal 退出（沙箱无公钥则无法安全运行）\n21: \n22: 2. **AuthMiddleware 中间件**\n23:    - 验证 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` 请求头\n24:    - 使用 RS256 算法验证 JWT 签名，拒绝 HMAC 等非 RSA 签名方法\n25:    - 强制校验 `exp`（过期时间）和 `iat`（签发时间）claim\n26:    - 配置 1 分钟时钟容差（leeway），容忍分布式系统中的时钟偏移\n27:    - 验证通过后，将请求 Body 包装为 `http.MaxBytesReader`（32 MiB 限制）\n28:    - 验证失败返回标准化 401 JSON 响应\n29: \n30: 3. **路由集成**\n31:    - 将 `AuthMiddleware` 应用于 `/api` 路由组（execute、files 等所有业务端点）\n32:    - 健康检查端点 `/health` 保持在路由组外，不受认证保护（供 K8s liveness/readiness probe 使用）\n33:    - 中间件顺序：`gin.Logger()` → `gin.Recovery()` → `AuthMiddleware()` → Handler\n34: \n35: 4. **单元测试**\n36:    - 有效 JWT 请求正常放行（200）\n37:    - 过期 JWT 返回 401\n38:    - 缺少 Authorization 头返回 401\n39:    - 非 Bearer 类型 token 返回 401\n40:    - HMAC 签名（HS256）被拒绝，返回 401\n41:    - Body 大小限制生效验证\n42: \n43: ### 不包含\n44: \n45: - Router 端的 JWT 签发逻辑（由 AR-011 覆盖）\n46: - K8s Secret 密钥管理（Router 负责存储，PicoD 仅通过环境变量获取公钥）\n47: - RBAC / 基于角色的权限控制（仅做身份验证，不做授权）\n48: - JWT 刷新 / 续期机制（token 由 Router 在每次转发时重新签发）\n49: - mTLS 或其他传输层认证\n50: \n51: ## 架构概要\n52: \n53: ### 认证流程\n54: \n55: ```\n56: Client --> Router (验证客户端 JWT)\n57:          --> Router 签发新 JWT (RS256, 5min 过期)\n58:          --> PicoD (AuthMiddleware 验证 Router JWT)\n59:               --> 验证通过: 执行命令/文件操作\n60:               --> 验证失败: 返回 401\n61: ```\n62: \n63: ### AuthManager 设计\n64: \n65: ```go\n66: type AuthManager struct {\n67:     publicKey *rsa.PublicKey\n68:     mutex     sync.RWMutex\n69: }\n70: ```\n71: \n72: - **公钥加载**：启动时从 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量读取 PEM 编码的 RSA 公钥，解析后存储。加载失败则 Fatal 退出。\n73: - **线程安全**：使用 `sync.RWMutex` 保护公钥访问，支持未来热更新场景（当前为启动时一次性加载）。\n74: - **验证参数**：RS256 签名、强制 `exp`/`iat`、1 分钟 leeway，与 Router 端签发参数一致。\n75: \n76: ### 错误响应格式\n77: \n78: ```json\n79: {\n80:   \"error\": \"<human-readable message>\",\n81:   \"code\": 401,\n82:   \"detail\": \"<technical detail>\"\n83: }\n84: ```\n85: \n86: 错误场景：\n87: - 缺少 Authorization 头 → `\"Missing Authorization header\"`\n88: - 非 Bearer 格式 → `\"Invalid Authorization header format\"`\n89: - 签名无效 / 非 RSA 算法 → `\"Invalid token\"` + detail 包含具体错误\n90: - Token 过期 → `\"Invalid token\"` + detail 包含 `\"token is expired\"`\n91: \n92: ### 路由结构\n93: \n94: ```go\n95: engine.Use(gin.Logger(), gin.Recovery())\n96: \n97: api := engine.Group(\"/api\")\n98: api.Use(authManager.AuthMiddleware())\n99: {\n100:     api.POST(\"/execute\", ExecuteHandler)\n101:     api.POST(\"/files\", UploadFileHandler)\n102:     api.GET(\"/files\", ListFilesHandler)\n103:     api.GET(\"/files/*path\", DownloadFileHandler)\n104: }\n105: \n106: engine.GET(\"/health\", HealthCheckHandler)  // 无认证\n107: ```\n108: \n109: ### 目录结构\n110: \n111: ```\n112: pkg/picod/\n113: ├── auth.go           # AuthManager + AuthMiddleware\n114: ├── auth_test.go      # 单元测试\n115: ├── server.go         # Server（注册 AuthMiddleware）\n116: ├── types.go          # 常量定义（PublicKeyEnvVar, MaxBodySize）\n117: └── ...\n118: ```\n119: \n120: ## 影响分析\n121: \n122: ### 直接影响\n123: \n124: | 组件 | 影响 |\n125: |------|------|\n126: | `pkg/picod/auth.go` | 新增：AuthManager、AuthMiddleware |\n127: | `pkg/picod/auth_test.go` | 新增：AuthMiddleware 单元测试 |\n128: | `pkg/picod/server.go` | 修改：Server 结构体增加 authManager 字段，NewServer 初始化 AuthManager，registerRoutes 应用中间件 |\n129: | `pkg/picod/types.go` | 修改：增加 `PublicKeyEnvVar` 常量 |\n130: | `cmd/picod/main.go` | 无影响：NewServer 已封装认证初始化 |\n131: \n132: ### 上游依赖\n133: \n134: | 依赖 | 用途 | 影响 |\n135: |------|------|------|\n136: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` (v5.2.1) | JWT 解析与 RS256 验证 | 已有依赖，无新增 |\n137: | `crypto/rsa` / `crypto/x509` | RSA 公钥解析 | Go 标准库，无新增 |\n138: | `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | HTTP 中间件框架 | 已有依赖，无新增 |\n139: \n140: ### 下游依赖\n141: \n142: | 组件 | 影响 |\n143: |------|------|\n144: | Router | 无影响。Router 已在转发时签发 JWT（AR-011） |\n145: | WorkloadManager | 无影响。负责将 Router 公钥注入 PicoD 环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` |\n146: | client-go | 无影响。client-go 仅用于 CRD 操作，不直接调用 PicoD API |\n147: | 沙箱内 Agent | 无直接影响。Agent 通过 Router 代理访问 PicoD，不直接调用 |\n148: \n149: ### 风险评估\n150: \n151: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n152: |------|------|----------|\n153: | 公钥环境变量未设置导致 PicoD 启动失败 | 高 | 设计预期：无公钥则不应启动；WorkloadManager 负责注入 |\n154: | Router 密钥轮换后 PicoD 仍使用旧公钥 | 中 | 当前为启动时一次性加载；密钥轮换需重建沙箱 Pod |\n155: | RS256 验证延迟影响 PicoD 吞吐 | 低 | 单次验证约 0.1-0.3ms，对沙箱内延迟影响可忽略 |\n156: | 时钟偏移导致有效 token 被拒绝 | 低 | 1 分钟 leeway 覆盖常见时钟偏移 |\n157: \n158: ### 与现有组件的交互\n159: \n160: | 组件 | 交互方式 | 影响 |\n161: |------|----------|------|\n162: | Router JWTManager | Router 使用 RSA 私钥签发 token，PicoD 使用对应公钥验证 | 共享同一密钥对，通过 K8s Secret 分发 |\n163: | WorkloadManager | 从 `picod-router-identity` Secret 读取公钥，注入 PicoD 容器环境变量 | 无影响。WorkloadManager 已有此逻辑 |\n164: | AR-011 (Router JWT) | Router 端 JWT 签发与认证 | 互补关系：Router 签发 → PicoD 验证，形成完整认证链路 |\n165: \n166: ## 备选方案\n167: \n168: ### 1. 环境变量 + RS256 验证中间件（✅ 选定方案）\n169: \n170: **做法**：通过环境变量传递 RSA 公钥，在 Gin 中间件层验证 JWT 签名。\n171: \n172: **优点**：\n173: - 实现简单，改动集中在 2 个文件（auth.go + server.go）\n174: - 与 Router 端使用相同的密钥对和验证参数，保持一致性\n175: - 无外部依赖，沙箱内无需访问 K8s API\n176: - 验证逻辑与 AR-011 Router AuthMiddleware 模式统一\n177: \n178: **缺点**：\n179: - 公钥仅在启动时加载，密钥轮换需重建 Pod\n180: - 环境变量传递公钥在日志中可能泄露（需确保日志脱敏）\n181: \n182: **决策**：采用。与现有架构最契合，变更范围可控（S 级），满足安全需求。\n183: \n184: ### 2. K8s Secret 直接读取\n185: \n186: **做法**：PicoD 启动时通过 in-cluster client 直接读取 K8s Secret 获取公钥。\n187: \n188: **优点**：支持密钥热更新，无需重建 Pod  \n189: **缺点**：沙箱容器需绑定 ServiceAccount 和 RBAC 权限，增加攻击面；引入 K8s client 依赖  \n190: **决策**：不采用。沙箱应最小化权限，不应直接访问 K8s API。\n191: \n192: ### 3. Unix Domain Socket 认证\n193: \n194: **做法**：PicoD 仅监听 Unix Domain Socket，通过文件系统权限控制访问。\n195: \n196: **优点**：无需 JWT，传输层安全  \n197: **缺点**：Router 与 PicoD 需在同一 Pod 内（当前架构满足），但无法支持未来跨 Pod 场景；与现有 HTTP 接口不兼容  \n198: **决策**：不采用。当前架构中 Router 通过 HTTP 转发到 PicoD Service，需保持 HTTP 接口。\n199: \n200: ### 4. mTLS 双向认证\n201: \n202: **做法**：PicoD 启用 TLS，Router 提供客户端证书。\n203: \n204: **优点**：传输层加密 + 双向身份验证  \n205: **缺点**：证书管理复杂；沙箱内 TLS 终止增加资源消耗；与现有 JWT 体系重复  \n206: **决策**：不采用。可在应用层 JWT 认证之上叠加，无需替代现有方案。\n207: \n208: ## 实现要点\n209: \n210: ### 常量定义\n211: \n212: ```go\n213: const (\n214:     PublicKeyEnvVar = \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"\n215:     MaxBodySize     = 32 << 20  // 32 MiB\n216: )\n217: ```\n218: \n219: ### AuthMiddleware 核心逻辑\n220: \n221: 1. 提取 `Authorization` 头，校验 `Bearer` 前缀\n222: 2. 调用 `jwt.Parse()` 验证签名，KeyFunc 中检查签名方法必须为 `*jwt.SigningMethodRSA`\n223: 3. 使用 `jwt.WithExpirationRequired()`、`jwt.WithIssuedAt()`、`jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute)` 选项\n224: 4. 验证失败统一返回 401 JSON，detail 字段包含具体错误信息\n225: 5. 验证通过后包装 `c.Request.Body` 为 `http.MaxBytesReader`\n226: \n227: ### Server 初始化\n228: \n229: ```go\n230: authManager := newAuthManager()\n231: if err := authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv(); err != nil {\n232:     checkFatal(err)  // 公钥加载失败则 Fatal 退出\n233: }\n234: ```\n235: \n236: ### 测试策略\n237: \n238: - 使用 `rsa.GenerateKey()` 生成临时密钥对，公钥设置到 AuthManager，私钥签署测试 token\n239: - 覆盖所有错误分支：缺失 header、格式错误、过期、非 RSA 签名\n240: - 验证 Body 大小限制在认证通过后生效\n241: \n242: ## 验收标准\n243: \n244: 1. **认证中间件**\n245:    - [ ] `AuthMiddleware` 正确验证有效 JWT 并放行请求\n246:    - [ ] 过期 JWT 返回 401\n247:    - [ ] 缺少 Authorization 头返回 401\n248:    - [ ] 非 Bearer 类型 token 返回 401\n249:    - [ ] HMAC 签名（HS256）被拒绝，返回 401\n250:    - [ ] 验证通过后 Body 被 MaxBytesReader 包装\n251: \n252: 2. **公钥加载**\n253:    - [ ] 从 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量正确加载 RSA 公钥\n254:    - [ ] 环境变量未设置时返回错误\n255:    - [ ] 非 PEM 格式返回错误\n256: \n257: 3. **路由集成**\n258:    - [ ] `/api` 路由组受 AuthMiddleware 保护\n259:    - [ ] `/health` 端点保持公开，无需认证\n260: \n261: 4. **测试覆盖**\n262:    - [ ] 所有新增代码行覆盖率达到 80% 以上\n263:    - [ ] `go test ./pkg/picod/...` 全部通过\n264: \n265: ## 状态\n266: \n267: - [ ] 提案审查\n268: - [ ] 实现\n269: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 269 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件\n\n**Module:** pkg/picod\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** S\n\n## 目的\n\n为 AgentCube PicoD 沙箱守护进程添加 JWT 认证中间件，确保只有经过 Router 签发的合法请求才能执行命令和访问文件。当前 PicoD 的所有 `/api` 端点缺乏认证保护，任何网络可达的客户端均可直接调用沙箱资源，存在严重的安全风险。\n\nPicoD 运行在每个沙箱 Pod 内部，负责命令执行和文件管理。由于沙箱网络可能被同一 Namespace 内的其他 Pod 访问，必须通过 JWT 验证请求来源为合法的 Router 实例，防止未授权的沙箱资源滥用。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n\n1. **AuthManager 实现**\n   - `AuthManager` 结构体：持有 RSA 公钥和读写锁，支持线程安全的密钥访问\n   - `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()`：从 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量加载 PEM 格式的 RSA 公钥\n   - 启动时强制加载公钥，失败则 Fatal 退出（沙箱无公钥则无法安全运行）","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775845811576,"end":1775845811582}}}}
